summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller to execute a quit-claim deed to Antonio Turner for lot 8, less the west 114 feet, of block 9, H. L. Yesler's 2nd Addition to the City of Seattle, in consideration of the re-payment to the City of Seattle, by said Antonio Turner, of certain moneys paid to the Treasurer of King County, for general taxes.
